room_title: Escape room "Last Breath" by Operation Outbreak in El Paso
room_address: 4530 Montana Suite E El Paso, TX 79903
room_description: In the late 2000’s and 2010’s, fear grips the city of El Paso as a serial killer stalks its residents. He has claimed victim after victim and taunts the authorities with cryptic messages, cyphers and menacing phone calls. His latest target is your best friend and he has taken him hostage, he however has given you one last chance to rescue him. Find out where he is located before he takes his last breath.
